TODAY'S QUOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"I guess somebody doesn't like democracy." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Tom Van Sant, the artist who designed Los Angeles' replica of the Beijing 
students' "Goddess of Democracy" statue, after learning that vandals had 
destroyed his monument to the original. 
</P>
