<P>
U.S. STRATEGY FOR NUCLEAR RESPONSE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Words cannot begin to express my feelings upon reading your account of the Bush 
Administration's latest nuclear strategy, a plan called SIOP-7. 
</P>
<P>
Words like shock, anger, fear, outrage, sadness and laughter. They can't be 
serious -- there must be something funny about this. Yes -- the joke's on us 
mere mortal taxpayers. 
</P>
<P>
When are they going to stop this waste? When are we? 
</P>
<P>
HAROLD WITTNER 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
