<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA080189-0027 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 89323 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 1, 1989, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part 5; Page 3; Column 1; View Desk 
