PROPOSITION 99 (TOBACCO TAX); WELFARE PROGRAMS -- CALIFORNIA; LOBBYING; TOBACCO 
INDUSTRY; HEALTH EDUCATION; EXCISE TAX -- CALIFORNIA; ISSUE ADVERTISING; FEUDS; 
