<TEXT>
<P>
The man who shot and wounded a Beverly Hills banker during a robbery at the 
banker's condominium Sunday may have been the same gunman who shot 48-year-old 
Andre Coffyn to death July 10 during a robbery at Coffyn's Michel Richard 
restaurant in the Wilshire District, police said Monday. 
</P>
