ATHLETES -- ELIGIBILITY; SPORTS RULES AND REGULATIONS; INTERNATIONAL OLYMPIC 
COMMITTEE; UNITED STATES OLYMPIC COMMITTEE; SUSPENSIONS; AMATEUR ATHLETIC 
