trial date will be set. 
</P>
<P>
Many of the teen-age girls told of inappropriate sexual comments or touching 
incidents by Denny while they were in custody at Juvenile Hall. The victims 
were then all 15 to 17 years old. Denny was charged with the offenses in May. 
