</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA080189-0105 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 89521 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 1, 1989, Tuesday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part 4; Page 2B; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
