DEVELOPERS; UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; PROPERTY SALES; LYON, 
WILLIAM; DEPARTMENT OF HOUSING AND URBAN DEVELOPMENT (U.S.); INVESTIGATIONS; 
COMPLAINTS; WISEMAN, SHIRLEY MCVAY; WILLIAM LYON CO 
</P>
